<h2>Notice &mdash; FPDF acknowledgment</h2>
<p>
    The <code>EgoPDF.Generator</code> package is an evolution of an automated
    C# port of <a href="https://www.fpdf.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FPDF</a>,
